savol
modern blog & community api

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. modellar arxitekturasi(database design)
siz quyidagi model strukturasini yaratishingiz va ular orasidagi bogliqliklarni togri ornatishingiz kerak:

Category: name(unique), slug.
Tag: name(unique)
Post:
author(User FK).
category (Category FK, related_name='posts)
tags (ManyToManyField)
title, content, created_at, views_count(default=0)

Like:
user(User FK).
post(Post FK, related_name='likes').

Constraint: Bitta foydalanuvchi bitta postga faqat 1 marta like bosa olishini ma'lumotlar bazasi darajasida ta'minlag(UniqueConstraint).
