2. Serializers (Logic & Custom Fields)
PostSerializer quyidagi talablarga javob berishi shart:

Custom Fields:
likes_count: Postga tegishli like lar soni (Annotation orqali hisoblansin).
is_liked: So'rov yuborgan foydalanuvchi(request.user) ushbu postga like bosganmi yoki yoqmi (Boolean).

Writable Nested Logic:
tags maydoni stringlar ro'yxati korinishida qabul qilinsin (masalan: ["python", "django"]).
create() va update() metodlarini override qiling: agar jonatilgan tag bazada bolmasa, yangi yaratsin (get_or_create), bor bolsa postga biriktirsin.
Read-only: views_count va author foydalanuvchi tomonidan qolda ozgartirilmasligi kerak.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅
