---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. Custom Permissions (Acees Control)
Faqatgina IsAuthenticatedOrReadOnly yetarli emas. Quyidagi talablarga mos IsAuthorOrAdminOrReadOnly nomli ruxsatnoma yarating:
GET (Hamma): Postlarni hamma kora oladi (anonim foydalanuvchilar ham).
POST (Authenticated): Post yaratish uchun foydalanuvchi login qilgan bolishi shart.
PUT/PATCH (Author/Admin): Postni faqat uning muallifi yoki Admin ozgartira oladi.
DELETE (Admin only): Postni faqat Admin ochira oladi.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------



4. ViewSet & Action Logic

PostViewSet ichida standart CRUD ammallaridan tashqari quyidagilarni bajaring:
Custom Action (/like/): Post sorovi orqali postga like bosish yoki like ni qaytarib olish (toggle logic) funksiyasini yozing.
Custom Action (/my-posts/): Faqat joriy login qilgan foydalanuvchining postlarini qaytaruvchi endpoint.
Retrieve Logic: Har safar bitta post tafsilotlarini korilganda (retrieve), views_count maydonini 1 taga oshiring.

