---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

5. Filtering, Search & Ordering
API foydalanuvchilari malumotlarni oson topishlari uchun:
Filtering: django-filter kutubxonasidan foydalanib, category (id boyicha) va tags (slug yoki nomi boyicha) filtrlashni yolga qoying.
Search: title va content maydonlari boyicha qidirish.
Ordering: created_at (yangi/eski) va views_count (ommaboplik) boyicha tartiblash.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅✅
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------




6. Django Admin & Optimization
Admin Panel: Postlar royxati views_count korinsin, lekin uni admin ham qolda tahrirlay olmasin (readonly_fields). Like larni post ichida Inline korinishida qoshing.
Optimization (N+1 problem): get_queryset metodida select_related (category, author uchun) va prefetch_related(tags uchun) ishlating.
Slug Generation: Post yaratilayotgan paytda titledan kelib chiqib avtomatic slug generatsiya qiling (agar modelda slug bolsa).
Dynamic Fields: Agar serializerga ?/fields=id, title deb sorov kelsa, faqat osha maydonlarni qaytarsin.
